      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kingston%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Kingston once hosted four railroad companies and two trolley lines, and today the Hudson River Maritime Museum and Trolley Museum honor that transport legacy.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
